<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT63">
<l>tarittiruntē ṉākavē tārā kaṇappōr</l>
<l>viritturaitta veṉṉākat tuṉṉai teritteḻuti</l>
<l>vācittuṅ kēṭṭum vaṇaṅki vaḻipaṭṭum</l>
<l>pūcittum pōkkiṉēṉ pōtu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I have spent time speaking of, writing about,</l>
<l>Reading, hearing about, bowing to, worshipping, and showing devotion to</l>
<l>You on the cruel serpent that spoke extensively about the movement</l>
<l rend="indent">of stellar constellations.</l>
<l>Therefore, I have borne patiently [with this life].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
